<p style="text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体"><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 如浅卧于杯中的一颗红宝石，香气丰厚、渗透性强，酒体醇厚、肥硕、入口有层次感，复合而协调。适合独酌，佐餐以香料炖煮的肉类，尤其是美味香浓的火锅、口感浓郁的野味，或配以麻辣为主的川菜，香浓的麻辣与强劲的单宁给人美好感觉。</span></span></span></p>
</span></span></span></span>
<p style="text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>
<span style="font-family: 宋体"><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">
<p><span style="color: #800080"><span style="font-size: 16px"><strong><span style="line-height: 200%"><img alt="" src="http://pic.womai.com/online/goods/header/hongjiu/ptjxcs.jpg" /></span></strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #0000ff"><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#9658;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">品酒的酒杯要干净而透明，倒酒不应太满，只倒入酒杯深度的1/3就可以了。&nbsp; <br />
<span style="color: #0000ff"><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#9658;</span></span></span> 白色桌布最适合鉴赏葡萄酒的颜色。&nbsp; <br />
<span style="color: #0000ff"><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#9658; </span></span></span>葡萄酒的酒杯以郁金香型或圆形缩口高脚玻璃杯或水晶杯较好，以便能摇动葡萄酒，使葡萄酒的香气在出杯口前浓缩。&nbsp;<br />
<span style="color: #0000ff"><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#9658;</span></span></span> 持酒杯的杯脚或杯柄，而不要握住酒杯的杯壁，否则会使酒温升高而影响葡萄酒的香气和口感。&nbsp; <br />
<span style="color: #0000ff"><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#9658; </span></span></span>喝白葡萄酒或香槟汽酒前冰镇一个小时左右的时间，让酒的温度保持在12℃左右口味更好；如果是红葡萄酒，一般不冰镇，也不加冰，正常室温下(16-18℃)饮用即可。</span></span></p>
