<p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑"><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family: 宋体"><span style="font-size: 16px"><strong><span><span style="line-height: 200%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 葡萄酒的分类&nbsp;<br />
</span></span></strong></span><span><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color: #800080"><strong>根据色泽<br />
</strong></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 可分为红葡萄酒、白葡萄酒、桃红葡萄酒三类。其中，白葡萄酒并非白色，一般</span></span></span><span><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">为浅禾秆黄色，桃红葡萄酒色泽则比红葡萄酒稍淡。&nbsp;<br />
<span style="color: #800080"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;根据糖度<br />
</strong></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 可分为干型、半干型、甜型、半甜型四类。<br />
<span style="color: #800080"><span style="background-color: #ffffff"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;根据酒中二氧化碳的压力<br />
</strong></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 按照酒中二氧化碳含量（以压力表示）可以将葡萄酒分为平静葡萄酒、起泡葡萄</span></span></span><span><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">酒、加气起泡葡萄酒。<br />
<span style="color: #800080"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;特种葡萄酒<br />
</strong></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 用鲜葡萄或葡萄汁在采摘或酿造工艺中使用特定方法酿制而成的葡萄酒。如：冰</span></span></span><span><span style="line-height: 200%"><span style="font-size: 14px">葡萄酒、贵腐葡萄酒等等</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
